            <h3>EARTH</h3>
            <p>
              Earth is the third planet from the Sun and the only astronomical object known to harbor life. According to radiometric dating and other
               sources of evidence, Earth formed over 4.5 billion years ago. Earth's gravity interacts with other objects in space,
               especially the Sun and the Moon, which is Earth's only natural satellite.
            </p>
